  "description": "Zapekanka (запеканка) is a Russian village cheesecake made of cottage cheese (tvorog, творог) and smetana (сметана). It's less sweet and smooth than the New York cheesecake and makes a great breakfast (if you cook it the evening before) topped with some marmalade and fresh berries. (And don't forget to brew a cup of [café de olla](/recipes/cafe-de-olla/)!)",
