  "keywords": [],
  "notes": [
    "You could buy both cottage cheese (tvorog) and smetana in any [Russian store](/shops/).",
    "You could replace honey and vanilla extract in the base with 35 g of date syrup."
  ],
  "overnight": false,
  "slug": "cottage-cheesecake",
  "source": "This recipe is based on a recipe from [Viktoria Melnik’s](https://www.instagram.com/vicky_bakery/) book “Food as it is”.",
  "steps": [
    {
      "name": "To cook the base",
      "steps": [
        {
          "text": "Preheat oven to 170C.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Mix cottage cheese (tvorog) using a food processor or push it through a sieve to smoothen the grains.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "In a big mixing bowl, combine <Ingredient name=\"egg\"  /> and <Ingredient name=\"honey\"  /> until you have fluffy light beige mass, using a mixer.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the cottage cheese of step 2, <Ingredient name=\"corn starch\"  />, <Ingredient name=\"vanilla extract\"  />, and zest of <Ingredient name=\"lime\"  />, then mix using a silicone spatula.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add <Ingredient name=\"smetana\"  /> and mix again.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Put baking paper onto the bottom of the baking form and butter its sides.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Pour the mixture into the baking form.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Bake 10-20 minutes.",
          "pause": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "To finish zapekanka",
      "steps": [
        {
          "text": "While the base is baking, prepare the topping. Mix <Ingredient name=\"smetana\"  />, <Ingredient name=\"egg\"  />, <Ingredient name=\"honey\"  />, <Ingredient name=\"vanilla extract\"  />, and juice of <Ingredient name=\"lime\"  /> using a mixer.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Pour the topping on top of the base, and bake for 30-40 minutes more.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Cool down the cake in a turned-off oven and then refrigerate for about 1 hour.",
          "pause": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
